<script id="record-template" type="text/x-handlebars-template">
<table class="table table-striped">
	<tr>
		<th width="200">Author</th>
		<td>\{{record.user.username}}</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<th width="200">Aufgenommen von</th>
		<td>\{{record.reporter.username}}</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<th width="200">Aufgenommen am</th>
		<td>\{{formatDate submitted}} \{{formatTime submitted}}</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<th width="200">Dauer</th>
		<td>\{{fixed2 record.duration}}s</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<th width="200">Text</th>
		<td>\{{record.quote}}</td>
	</tr>
</table>
</script>
<h1>Aufnahme Forken</h1>
<p>Hier können Aufnahmen modifiziert und als neue Aufnahmen gespeichert werden.</p>
<h2>Info</h2>
<div id="record-info"></div>

<h2>Editor</h2>
<div class="fork-box">
	<div class="slider slider-begin">
		<div class="head">0.0s</div>
		<div class="leg"></div>
	</div>
	<div class="slider slider-end">
		<div class="head">0.0s</div>
		<div class="leg"></div>
	</div>
	<div class="slider slider-indicator">
		<div class="leg"></div>
	</div>
	<div class="box box-left"></div>
	<div class="box box-right"></div>
	<canvas id="timeline-canvas"></canvas>
	<canvas id="fork-canvas"></canvas>
</div>

<h2>Daten</h2>
<form class="form-horizontal">
	<div class="form-group">
		<label for="play" class="col-sm-2 control-label">Abspielen</label>
		<div class="col-sm-10">
			<button class="btn btn-primary disabled" id="play"> <i class="fa fa-volume-up"></i> Play</button>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="form-group">
		<label for="overwrite" class="col-sm-2 control-label">Überschreiben</label>
		<div class="col-sm-10">
			<input type="checkbox" value="overwrite" id="overwrite"/>
			Aktivieren, wenn die originale Aufnahme durch diese Aufnahme überschrieben werden soll, anstatt eine neue Aufnahme anzulegen.
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="form-group">
		<label for="description" class="col-sm-2 control-label">Beschreibung</label>
		<div class="col-sm-10">
			<div class="input-group">
				<span class="input-group-addon"><i class="fa fa-edit"></i></span>
				<textarea style="resize: none;" rows="3" name="description" class="form-control" id="description"></textarea>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="form-group">
		<label for="save" class="col-sm-2 control-label">Speichern</label>
		<div class="col-sm-10">
			<button class="btn btn-success" type="button" id="submit"><i class="fa fa-save"></i> Speichern</button>
		</div>
	</div>
</form>
<script src="/dist/record/fork.js"></script>
